1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:09,110
Step down

3
00:00:10,040 --> 00:00:12,840
from your position as the president immediately.

4
00:00:14,630 --> 00:00:15,470
You...

5
00:00:17,470 --> 00:00:18,310
are done for.

6
00:00:18,310 --> 00:00:19,670
Are you crazy?

7
00:00:19,670 --> 00:00:21,670
What did the Ning family do to you?

8
00:00:21,670 --> 00:00:23,920
Did you do all this for your benefit?

9
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:25,480
Why are you doing this to me?

10
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:26,990
I'm your medicine.

11
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,500
Why look for me for such a trivial matter?

12
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:32,830
What did I raise you for?

13
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:34,160
Hello, Song Yu.

14
00:00:34,430 --> 00:00:36,030
Investigate someone for me.

15
00:00:45,270 --> 00:00:46,270
A brocade banner?

16
00:00:46,670 --> 00:00:47,350
For whom?

17
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:48,710
A gift from our fans.

18
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:51,270
That's a good thing, sir.

19
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:53,300
-You should be happy.
-Open it.

20
00:00:57,180 --> 00:00:59,950
To "Perfect Her" Editorial Department.

21
00:00:59,990 --> 00:01:00,510
Yes.

22
00:01:00,870 --> 00:01:02,070
Such a genius editor,

23
00:01:02,190 --> 00:01:03,640
great ideas.

24
00:01:03,910 --> 00:01:04,510
Go on.

25
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,950
Dumb ass storyline.

26
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:10,170
Gives me high blood pressure.

27
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:12,710
From the second female lead's fans.

28
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:15,600
The second female lead's fans are sending us blades.

29
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,260
What do you think we should do?

30
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:19,030
Next chapter.

31
00:01:19,470 --> 00:01:20,190
Sir.

32
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:24,510
I won't let you and the audience down in the next chapter.

33
00:01:25,950 --> 00:01:26,990
You'd better.

34
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:03,280
[Perfect Her]

35
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:06,560
[Episode 18]

36
00:03:13,230 --> 00:03:13,830
Boss,

37
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:16,829
the lady you asked me to investigate who splashed water

38
00:03:16,829 --> 00:03:19,470
at Ms. Ning on Ning Zhaoxiong's 60th birthday is called Zhao Si.

39
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:21,550
She's the sister of Ms. Ning's ex

40
00:03:21,550 --> 00:03:23,670
who allegedly passed on after she abandoned him.

41
00:03:23,670 --> 00:03:26,120
She was also the first person who released the news online.

42
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,520
Zhao Lin died of illness.

43
00:03:27,670 --> 00:03:29,480
Zhao Si blamed all of this

44
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,630
on Ms. Ning.

45
00:03:32,350 --> 00:03:34,440
According to what she said,

46
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,630
it was Ms. Bai Li who looked for her.

47
00:03:36,790 --> 00:03:38,510
The follow-up scandals about Ms. Ning

48
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:40,310
were also provided by Ms. Bai Li.

49
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:45,440
She also arranged those photos taken at the hotel, and venue setting,

50
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:47,040
under the order of Ms. Bai Li.

51
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:49,550
Anything else?

52
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,880
Zhao Si is also mentally ill.

53
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:53,470
She's Dr. Peng Yu's patient.

54
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,240
She had counseling with him.

55
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,870
All the people related to this

56
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,360
are all his patients.

57
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:02,040
Yes.

58
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:04,150
There's something more interesting.

59
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:06,510
Ms. Bai and Yang Group's young master Yang Guang

60
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:08,140
set up a fund recruitment company

61
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,150
named BY Group.

62
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:11,470
The 55% shares that Ningmei holds now

63
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:13,400
was what forced Ning Zhaoxiong

64
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,350
to pass the CEO position to Ms. Bai

65
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,670
at the board meeting.

66
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,390
Bai Li went to the company

67
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,870
and forced Ning Zhaoxiong to quit.

68
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:21,470
Yes.

69
00:04:21,709 --> 00:04:23,510
There were many people there.

70
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:26,310
Ms. Bai lashed out on Ning Zhaoxiong.

71
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:28,520
She's not simple.

72
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:30,520
She's smart and ruthless.

73
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,270
Boss, are you okay?

74
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:33,990
What should we do next?

75
00:04:33,990 --> 00:04:34,650
To Ningmei.

76
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:43,890
Give me the pen.

77
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,030
Ms. Bai,

78
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,730
please take a closer look.

79
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,010
Especially Article 6.

80
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,750
You need to confirm it yourself.

81
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,110
We don't dare to decide it.

82
00:04:52,110 --> 00:04:53,570
You are the legal counsel.

83
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,270
I paid you

84
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:56,870
to do nothing?

85
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,590
Why didn't you edit the contract before passing it to me?

86
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:01,490
Ms. Bai,

87
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:04,390
I've negotiated this contract with the other party for three rounds.

88
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:06,560
This is the result after we compromised.

89
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,400
However,

90
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:11,230
Article 6, regarding the rights for the follow-up development of derivatives,

91
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:12,950
-are to be–
-It's theirs. It's settled then.

92
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,150
We can't do that, Ms. Bai.

93
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:15,990
10% of our performance

94
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:18,450
is based on the development of derivatives.

95
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:20,280
10%?

96
00:05:21,250 --> 00:05:22,180
That's not much.

97
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:23,260
Ms. Bai,

98
00:05:23,330 --> 00:05:25,720
I think you were too busy to take a look.

99
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:28,110
Our cooperation

100
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,750
would takes three years to improve our performance.

101
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,870
But the loss of 10%

102
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,520
will easily cause a huge loss to this year's financial report.

103
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:36,780
So you don't understand what I'm saying?

104
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:38,870
Either I sign it,

105
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,530
or get lost.

106
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,460
Ms. Bai,

107
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,190
we'll leave first.

108
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,310
Get lost!

109
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,510
Let's go.

110
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,950
Signing the contract

111
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,700
is just a process.

112
00:06:10,670 --> 00:06:12,540
The most important thing in cooperation

113
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,540
is the early stages of negotiation.

114
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,120
Su Yu, why are you here?

115
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,010
Bai Li,

116
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:25,360
you've never handled these things yourself.

117
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,090
Don't worry.

118
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:27,480
You can learn it slowly.

119
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,510
As you know,

120
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:34,110
Ye Yunkai didn't allow me to interfere in the company's operation.

121
00:06:35,150 --> 00:06:38,110
Actually, sometimes I'm a little bit naive.

122
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:40,310
But you don't seem naive

123
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:43,060
from what you did previously.

124
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:45,520
What do you mean?

125
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:48,040
On May 21, you first came to Ningmei

126
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:50,070
to negotiate with Ning Zhaoxiong.

127
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:51,110
On May 29,

128
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:54,370
all the scandals about Ning Mochen were spread online.

129
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:55,200
Then,

130
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:58,360
all the scandals were exposed at Ning Zhaoxiong's birthday banquet.

131
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,760
Ningmei's stocks also plummeted that day.

132
00:07:01,110 --> 00:07:02,100
On June 1,

133
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:06,030
you and Yang Guang started BY Capital and started acquiring stocks crazily,

134
00:07:06,030 --> 00:07:09,290
buying all the Ningmei stocks in the market at a high price.

135
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:11,910
Although the purchase price is much higher than the market price,

136
00:07:11,910 --> 00:07:13,770
due to the decrease a few days ago,

137
00:07:13,990 --> 00:07:16,450
the stock price is at its historical lowest.

138
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,850
And then?

139
00:07:19,910 --> 00:07:20,950
On June 3rd,

140
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:23,870
you forced Ning Zhaoxiong to resign at the board meeting

141
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:25,600
and gained control of Ningmei.

142
00:07:25,710 --> 00:07:27,310
Weren't you behind all this?

143
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,510
You investigated me?

144
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,270
Bai Li.

145
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:35,470
Why did you do that?

146
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,150
I told you

147
00:07:38,790 --> 00:07:41,470
Ning Mochen forced me to do this.

148
00:07:43,590 --> 00:07:45,320
Even if Ning Mochen forced you,

149
00:07:46,150 --> 00:07:46,950
you just recovered

150
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,230
you just recovered and lost your memory.

151
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:49,830
You wouldn't have done that.

152
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,220
What are you trying to tell me?

153
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:58,070
Why did you pretend to have amnesia?

154
00:07:58,550 --> 00:07:59,510
Why did you frame her?

155
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:00,830
I framed her?

156
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:04,350
Ning Mochen deserves it.

157
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,440
None of the exposes are fake.

158
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,330
You should know

159
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:12,060
what she did to me.

160
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,950
She ruined my family

161
00:08:16,650 --> 00:08:18,040
and my life.

162
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:21,160
How can I let her go so easily?

163
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:24,400
Of course I want her to lose everything.

164
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,250
I wanted to let her feel

165
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:28,420
the feeling of being isolated.

166
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,150
Now I did it.

167
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,159
Shouldn't you be happy for me?

168
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,190
Bai Li.

169
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:38,150
How did you become like this?

170
00:08:38,830 --> 00:08:40,090
The Bai Li I knew before

171
00:08:40,299 --> 00:08:41,690
wouldn't be so cruel.

172
00:08:42,539 --> 00:08:43,480
Do you know how many innocent people

173
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,320
you will affect by manipulating the stocks?

174
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,380
So good people should be suppressed?

175
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:51,100
If I'm bullied, shouldn't I fight back?

176
00:08:51,660 --> 00:08:54,060
You always wanted to uphold justice for me.

177
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,790
Actually, we have the same goal.

178
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,830
The Bai Li I know

179
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,390
won't use others,

180
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,790
much less me.

181
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,810
I used you?

182
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,660
What have you done for me?

183
00:09:06,610 --> 00:09:07,930
Your soul

184
00:09:08,070 --> 00:09:09,960
has been seduced by Ning Mochen.

185
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:13,120
What about Ningmei?

186
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,110
Have you ever thought about running it well?

187
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:15,950
You snatched it

188
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:17,320
just to destroy it?

189
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,390
It has so many employees,

190
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:19,030
and they all have families.

191
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,750
What will they do if you ruin it?

192
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,070
It has nothing to do with you, an outsider.

193
00:09:22,070 --> 00:09:24,090
You don't have to tell me what to do!

194
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:28,760
An outsider?

195
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:31,640
Aren't you an outsider?

196
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,920
I can do whatever I want.

197
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:42,020
Who are you to tell me what to do?

198
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:43,540
Who do you think you are?

199
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:46,730
Let me tell you.

200
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:50,410
All of you are just my tools.

201
00:09:51,310 --> 00:09:53,500
You're useless now.

202
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,260
If you can read the room,

203
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,780
get lost immediately.

204
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,510
Bai Li,

205
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,010
your supper is here.

206
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:26,040
Get up and eat.

207
00:10:31,910 --> 00:10:33,590
Open it.

208
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:36,080
Don't you know how to read the room?

209
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:38,340
Stop sleeping and get up.

210
00:10:39,070 --> 00:10:41,730
You don't have any tableware you can use at home.

211
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,110
I brought you mine.

212
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:48,430
Get up.

213
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:53,680
Have some water.

214
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,730
What are you doing?

215
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,120
So ugly.

216
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:10,030
Why did you do that?

217
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,070
Shouldn't ugly things

218
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:17,150
disappear from this world?

219
00:11:21,570 --> 00:11:22,550
You too.

220
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,660
But you designed that cup personally

221
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,880
and made it for me as a birthday present.

222
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,390
But that doesn't change the fact

223
00:11:32,110 --> 00:11:34,130
that I think it's ugly now.

224
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,140
Bai Li,

225
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,560
I don't know what's wrong with you.

226
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,720
You've changed since you came out of the hospital.

227
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:03,280
You became selfish, indifferent,

228
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,850
and moody.

229
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:07,070
I really don't know how to help you.

230
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,190
I don't need your help.

231
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,170
I crossed the line.

232
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:21,720
Maybe it's more suitable for you to live alone in the future.

233
00:12:25,190 --> 00:12:26,460
Our friendship

234
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,280
is over.

235
00:12:42,310 --> 00:12:43,350
You're leaving?

236
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,990
Go then.

237
00:12:50,190 --> 00:12:51,030
Go find her.

238
00:12:52,190 --> 00:12:53,310
Go find her.

239
00:12:54,830 --> 00:12:56,790
All of you, go find her, okay?

240
00:12:57,470 --> 00:12:58,970
Leave me alone!

241
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:30,620
[Ning Mochen]

242
00:13:51,590 --> 00:13:52,620
Ms. Ning!

243
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:57,210
Dinner is ready. Let's eat.

244
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:58,800
Jiang,

245
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:00,330
I don't have the appetite.

246
00:14:00,430 --> 00:14:01,110
Oh.

247
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:04,770
Are you missing Mr. Su?

248
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:08,410
I can't hide anything from you.

249
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,670
Ms. Ning,

250
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,220
I think

251
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:14,520
you don't have to worry about the girl who came two days ago.

252
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:16,720
What?

253
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:20,050
There's no love in the way she looks at Mr. Su.

254
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:21,870
Unlike the way you look at Mr. Su.

255
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,200
Your eyes are...

256
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:25,050
Of course.

257
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:28,320
Mr. Su also looks at you with love.

258
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:31,070
Not when he looked at that girl.

259
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:32,530
Jiang.

260
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:33,510
Oh.

261
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:34,630
Look at me.

262
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,690
I talked too much again.

263
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:38,780
But then again,

264
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:41,680
a person can lie with words,

265
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,150
but not with their gaze.

266
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:45,750
I think you have nothing to worry about.

267
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:48,950
Thank you, Jiang.

268
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:49,920
You're welcome.

269
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,230
Remember to eat.

270
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:52,870
It won't taste good if it gets cold.

271
00:14:52,870 --> 00:14:53,550
See you.

272
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:59,610
I wonder how Su Yu is doing.

273
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,750
I’m so useless.

274
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,840
I can't do anything

275
00:15:04,310 --> 00:15:05,550
but wait here.

276
00:15:11,010 --> 00:15:17,410
[For rent]

277
00:15:12,430 --> 00:15:13,160
Ning Mochen,

278
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:15,750
your heart is like an endless black hole

279
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:16,870
and a barren swamp.

280
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:26,310
[Lingyu Psychology Clinic]

281
00:15:17,710 --> 00:15:19,710
You always hold everyone around you

282
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:22,670
and drag them down with you.

