00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,600
I should have stayed away from you.

285
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:33,090
[For rent]

286
00:15:27,350 --> 00:15:31,080
I shouldn't have overestimated myself, thinking I could save you.

287
00:15:31,710 --> 00:15:32,800
From now on,

288
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:35,110
I hope both of us will be fine,

289
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:39,890
[Lingyu Psychology Clinic]

290
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,010
and will never meet again.

291
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:42,220
[For rent]

292
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:55,160
[Lingyu Psychology Clinic]

293
00:15:55,220 --> 00:15:59,360
[Jiusong Mountains and Rivers]
[Ningmei Jewelry Corporation]

294
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,110
Sir, you can't go in.

295
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:02,070
Without Ms. Bai's appointment–

296
00:16:02,070 --> 00:16:03,520
Do you know who I am?

297
00:16:08,790 --> 00:16:09,610
Go out.

298
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:15,360
Is it so hard to see you now?

299
00:16:16,390 --> 00:16:18,720
Since you became the chairman of Ningmei,

300
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,800
you don't answer my calls anymore.

301
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:22,110
You want to see me?

302
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,390
What's up?

303
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:25,160
How are you managing Ningmei?

304
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,380
In such a short time,

305
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:29,550
you have screwed it up.

306
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:31,150
I told you

307
00:16:31,170 --> 00:16:33,650
to report to me no matter what decision you make!

308
00:16:33,650 --> 00:16:34,580
Don't forget,

309
00:16:35,410 --> 00:16:36,970
we're just partners.

310
00:16:38,270 --> 00:16:39,950
You have no right to control me.

311
00:16:39,950 --> 00:16:40,830
Bai Li,

312
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:42,670
don't forget

313
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:45,510
who helped you up to this position.

314
00:16:57,190 --> 00:16:58,800
All right.

315
00:16:59,470 --> 00:17:01,030
Mr. Yang,

316
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,920
you didn't come to me

317
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:05,390
for such a trivial matter, right?

318
00:17:08,109 --> 00:17:09,270
Do you miss me?

319
00:17:16,349 --> 00:17:17,960
You still need me.

320
00:17:19,670 --> 00:17:20,630
I need you too.

321
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:27,569
Isn't Mr. Yang's favorite Ning Mochen?

322
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:29,510
When did you need me?

323
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,400
Chen

324
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:35,670
is engaged to her fiancé.

325
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:37,540
And I think

326
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:39,720
you are very similar to her.

327
00:17:41,430 --> 00:17:43,130
Hearing you say that

328
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:44,630
makes me sad.

329
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,570
I hate

330
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:50,170
orders and restrictions the most.

331
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:52,710
I don't belong to anyone.

332
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:54,880
I don't need anyone either.

333
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:56,730
Including you.

334
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:00,590
Oh...

335
00:18:01,710 --> 00:18:03,430
If I remember correctly,

336
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:06,370
your marriage is not over yet.

337
00:18:07,230 --> 00:18:10,150
That's why we can't be so close.

338
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,430
Why are you bringing that up?

339
00:18:11,430 --> 00:18:12,080
Oh, right.

340
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,670
I shouldn't

341
00:18:16,150 --> 00:18:17,550
call you Mr. Yang either.

342
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:19,110
I should call you

343
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:22,190
Mr. Song.

344
00:18:26,470 --> 00:18:27,930
What are you trying to say?

345
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:32,750
You are so boring.

346
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:35,650
I thought you were an interesting person,

347
00:18:35,950 --> 00:18:37,750
but you turned out to be nothing.

348
00:18:39,230 --> 00:18:40,770
Your name is Song Guang.

349
00:18:41,190 --> 00:18:42,950
You're a nobody.

350
00:18:43,630 --> 00:18:46,980
Later, with a pair of golden-rimmed glasses,

351
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:50,960
and pretending to be elegant and gentle,

352
00:18:51,150 --> 00:18:52,550
you attracted Ms. Yang.

353
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:56,640
She's the only daughter of the CEO of Tianyuan Capital.

354
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,240
Of course you can't miss her.

355
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:02,150
So you married into the Yang family

356
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,890
and changed your name

357
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:06,270
to Yang Guang.

358
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:10,790
Don't make it sound so bad.

359
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,540
We really loved each other back then.

360
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,630
After your father-in-law passed away,

361
00:19:15,630 --> 00:19:18,470
you used your wife to get most of the inheritance.

362
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:22,060
Now you want to divorce her suddenly.

363
00:19:22,710 --> 00:19:24,070
You call this true love?

364
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,070
What can we do?

365
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,900
We fell out of love.

366
00:19:27,230 --> 00:19:28,290
I find it a pity too.

367
00:19:28,310 --> 00:19:29,270
Fell out of love?

368
00:19:30,630 --> 00:19:32,110
Oh, right.

369
00:19:33,150 --> 00:19:36,070
You served them like a dog for 10 years.

370
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:39,510
Is it the love between a dog and its master?

371
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,510
Shut up.

372
00:19:53,450 --> 00:19:54,260
Why?

373
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:56,950
I got your pain point?

374
00:19:56,970 --> 00:19:58,760
I just want my name back.

375
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,430
What's wrong with that?

376
00:20:00,430 --> 00:20:03,970
You said you love Ning Mochen,

377
00:20:05,020 --> 00:20:06,960
but you still came to me.

378
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,670
No matter who you are,

379
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:12,800
or how rich you are,

380
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:14,370
you are a scum.

381
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:16,680
Do you think you deserve Ning Mochen?

382
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,370
So funny.

383
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:25,590
You're just a loser who relies on women at the end of the day!

384
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:26,070
I...

385
00:20:31,650 --> 00:20:32,650
I don't hit women.

386
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,780
But don't think I can do nothing to you.

387
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:37,390
Bai Li, remember,

388
00:20:38,390 --> 00:20:40,850
I am the actual person controlling Ningmei.

389
00:20:41,430 --> 00:20:43,290
If I can take you to that position,

390
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:46,880
means I can also make you fall from that position.

391
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:51,010
Let's see if you kick me down first

392
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:54,200
or I get to Yang family first.

393
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:02,430
See yourself out,

394
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:05,140
Mr. Song.

395
00:21:36,910 --> 00:21:37,910
Bai Li...

396
00:22:32,330 --> 00:22:35,640
[Tan's Silverware]

397
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:44,990
[Tan's Silverware]

398
00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:48,220
This kind of old-fashioned silverware shop is rare.

399
00:22:48,220 --> 00:22:49,390
If Su Yu were here,

400
00:22:49,410 --> 00:22:50,560
he'd be interested.

401
00:23:01,950 --> 00:23:03,390
This is...

402
00:23:03,570 --> 00:23:06,240
the ancient technique of embedding silver threads?

403
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,100
You know it too?

404
00:23:07,230 --> 00:23:08,710
I learned it in school.

405
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:10,200
But I've never tried it myself.

406
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:10,880
Is that so?

407
00:23:11,190 --> 00:23:12,390
Do you want to try?

408
00:23:12,470 --> 00:23:13,110
Sure.

409
00:23:13,310 --> 00:23:14,990
I'll buy it if I spoil it.

410
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:16,710
It's fine.

411
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:19,120
If I hadn't inherited this shop,

412
00:23:19,470 --> 00:23:21,840
I wouldn't be able to learn such good ancient skills.

413
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:23,030
Come, sit down.

414
00:23:23,150 --> 00:23:24,010
I'll teach you.

415
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:25,710
Thank you, Ma'am.

416
00:23:25,990 --> 00:23:26,990
Just call me Tan.

417
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:45,790
Ning Mochen.

418
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:48,350
Why would she make silverware?

419
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,970
Her posture and techniques

420
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:52,690
look familiar.

421
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:03,060
You're back.

422
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,680
How did it go with Bai Li?

423
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:10,010
I was sold this ring

424
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:11,720
for a thousand yuan.

425
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:13,920
Was I scammed?

426
00:24:16,430 --> 00:24:17,510
This ring...

427
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:21,370
The workmanship is indeed rough.

428
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:23,870
The parts they welded didn't join perfectly either.

429
00:24:23,870 --> 00:24:25,190
Look carefully.

430
00:24:25,210 --> 00:24:26,980
That is a design.

431
00:24:35,670 --> 00:24:36,350
Madam.

432
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:39,070
It's you again.

433
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:42,120
My friend was rude before.

434
00:24:42,320 --> 00:24:43,780
I apologize on her behalf.

435
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:46,150
I would like to buy something.

436
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,130
What is it?

437
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:50,200
The ring you made with that lady just now.

438
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:52,090
I'm sorry. I won't sell it.

439
00:24:52,710 --> 00:24:53,270
Why?

440
00:24:53,910 --> 00:24:55,710
Because I really like that lady.

441
00:24:55,710 --> 00:24:57,840
I don't want to sell something she made

442
00:24:58,060 --> 00:24:59,660
to someone I don't like.

443
00:25:00,170 --> 00:25:01,210
If I can tell you

444
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:03,070
the meaning of this ring,

445
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:04,980
will you sell it to me?

446
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:07,790
It depends on what you say.

447
00:25:07,940 --> 00:25:09,400
If you say something good,

448
00:25:09,710 --> 00:25:10,770
I'll sell it to you.

449
00:25:15,190 --> 00:25:16,750
The meaning of this ring is

450
00:25:17,870 --> 00:25:19,270
a meeting at a crossroad.

451
00:25:19,910 --> 00:25:21,480
The designer's concept is

452
00:25:22,550 --> 00:25:26,070
the two parallel lines that originally wouldn't interact

453
00:25:26,910 --> 00:25:28,860
meet by chance in a passing moment,

454
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:32,760
But having a different destination.

455
00:25:33,630 --> 00:25:34,790
The further they go,

456
00:25:35,630 --> 00:25:37,960
the two of them will only go further apart.

457
00:25:39,390 --> 00:25:40,390
That's what it is.

458
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:42,750
It sounds

459
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:44,410
quite pessimistic.

460
00:25:44,870 --> 00:25:45,980
Not pessimistic.

461
00:25:47,190 --> 00:25:48,070
Maybe

462
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:50,210
the creator wants to express that

463
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:52,810
destiny is unpredictable.

464
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:57,590
♫I want to give you all my dreams♫

465
00:25:57,190 --> 00:25:57,910
Ning Mochen.

466
00:25:57,690 --> 00:26:01,260
♫I can't hold on, can't hold on to the path of love♫

467
00:25:58,670 --> 00:26:00,870
Did something unbelievable

468
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:02,580
happen to you?

469
00:26:01,870 --> 00:26:07,540
♫What makes me so infatuated?♫

470
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,190
Why is your every move

471
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:09,340
just like Bai Li in my memory?

472
00:26:09,180 --> 00:26:12,300
♫You say love is like♫

473
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:12,150
Yet you have Ning Mochen's face.

474
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:16,440
♫Time devouring someone's memory♫

475
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:22,040
♫Even if I'm no longer me♫

476
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:18,230
Are you really

477
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:24,350
my senior, Bai Li?

478
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:27,690
♫And you're no longer you♫

479
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:29,590
Su Yu...

480
00:26:29,080 --> 00:26:34,030
♫I'm following you♫

481
00:26:32,670 --> 00:26:33,870
You finally

482
00:26:35,190 --> 00:26:36,310
recognize me.

483
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:41,690
♫All the things you do♫

484
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:40,780
Is it really you?

485
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:47,460
♫I'm running fast since I don't want to be late♫

486
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:51,410
♫Following the sparkling stars♫

487
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:56,750
♫I'm feeling my every breath♫

488
00:26:58,100 --> 00:27:03,070
♫You're everywhere♫

489
00:27:06,580 --> 00:27:07,720
Su Yu,

490
00:27:08,020 --> 00:27:08,910
listen to me.

491
00:27:08,910 --> 00:27:10,230
Hearing you speak

492
00:27:10,230 --> 00:27:11,510
makes me sick.

493
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:16,670
Ning Mochen, let me say it again.

494
00:27:16,670 --> 00:27:18,010
This is a fake engagement.

495
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:19,030
It's her.

496
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,090
She seduced my husband.

497
00:27:21,090 --> 00:27:22,590
Stop talking nonsense!

498
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:23,990
You called Su Yu here, didn’t you?

499
00:27:23,990 --> 00:27:24,790
You deliberately provoked me

500
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:25,990
just to act in front of him, right?

501
00:27:25,990 --> 00:27:26,580
Enough!

502
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:27,790
She wants to take this opportunity

503
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,270
to drag all of us down.

504
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:30,590
She's not Bai Li.

505
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:32,070
She's a lunatic.

506
00:27:32,150 --> 00:27:33,070
Enough.

507
00:27:36,430 --> 00:27:44,660
♫I'm following you♫

508
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:51,350
♫All the things you do♫

509
00:27:46,460 --> 00:27:47,270
You...

510
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:49,670
love Bai Li?

511
00:27:49,950 --> 00:27:50,510
Yes.

512
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,350
If Bai Li

513
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:54,790
never wakes up,

514
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:56,350
♫I'm running fast since I don't want to be late♫

515
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:57,110
what would you do?

516
00:27:57,230 --> 00:28:00,510
♫Following the sparkling stars♫

517
00:27:57,390 --> 00:27:59,050
I'll keep staying by her side.

518
00:27:59,670 --> 00:28:00,790
For how long?

519
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:05,800
♫I'm feeling my every breath♫

520
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:02,670
Forever?

521
00:28:06,450 --> 00:28:10,670
♫You're everywhere♫

522
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:22,710
You mean

523
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:25,250
you woke up in Ning Mochen's body

524
00:28:25,650 --> 00:28:27,060
and Ning Mochen

525
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,510
in yours?

526
00:28:31,110 --> 00:28:31,990
Bai Li,

527
00:28:32,300 --> 00:28:33,800
why didn't you tell me?

528
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,660
I don't know why

529
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:38,990
but every time when I want to tell the truth,

530
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:41,110
I feel dizzy,

531
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:42,870
my heart races,

532
00:28:43,060 --> 00:28:44,390
and I even go into shock.

533
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:45,850
What about now?

534
00:28:46,150 --> 00:28:47,680
How come nothing happened?

535
00:28:48,870 --> 00:28:50,400
Maybe it's because

536
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:52,360
you already recognized me.

537
00:28:54,210 --> 00:28:56,150
How could this happen?

538
00:28:57,990 --> 00:28:59,100
Do you remember

539
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:02,330
my 10th wedding anniversary?

540
00:29:03,610 --> 00:29:05,140
It should be that accident.

541
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:29,920
Everything makes sense now.

542
00:29:30,710 --> 00:29:33,180
Ning Mocheng used her own scoops

543
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:34,980
to affect Ningmei's stock price,

544
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,760
and then took the chance to acquire it,

545
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:38,100
and forced Ning Zhaoxiong to resign.

546
00:29:38,100 --> 00:29:40,620
She then used your body to create discord between the two of us.

547
00:29:40,620 --> 00:29:42,380
Ning Mochen used my body

548
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,160
to get what she wanted,

549
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:47,250
but she never thought

550
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,750
that there would be

551
00:29:49,140 --> 00:29:50,290
telepathy.

552
00:29:51,810 --> 00:29:53,180
I always believed

553
00:29:54,140 --> 00:29:55,510
you will find me.

554
00:29:58,600 --> 00:29:59,810
I'm sorry, Bai Li.

555
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:02,100
You reminded me a long time ago

556
00:30:02,330 --> 00:30:03,460
but I just realized.

557
00:30:04,820 --> 00:30:07,710
This is something unbelievable to start with anyway.

558
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:09,510
It's normal that you don't know.

559
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,630
It's a miracle that you can

560
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:14,830
recognize me now.

561
00:30:17,300 --> 00:30:18,300
You've suffered.

562
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,250
After I woke up,

563
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:26,120
I've been thinking about revenge

564
00:30:27,570 --> 00:30:29,570
and focused on playing Ning Mochen.

565
00:30:30,350 --> 00:30:33,340
But after so many things, I realized

566
00:30:34,610 --> 00:30:35,520
that

567
00:30:36,300 --> 00:30:40,070
revenge doesn't make me happy.

568
00:30:40,990 --> 00:30:44,270
Instead, it drags me into the abyss of pain.

569
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:46,240
Bai Li...

570
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,680
After everything is settled,

571
00:30:50,670 --> 00:30:52,000
I thought

572
00:30:52,630 --> 00:30:54,350
to go back to my life.

573
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:56,870
But I didn’t expect

574
00:30:57,250 --> 00:30:58,930
Ning Mochen suddenly woke up.

575
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:02,670
She even used my identity to use your feelings.

576
00:31:03,410 --> 00:31:05,460
I don't know what else she will do.

577
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:06,830
I'm really scared.

578
00:31:06,830 --> 00:31:07,590
Don't worry.

579
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,790
I finally found you.

580
00:31:10,180 --> 00:31:11,950
I won't let anyone hurt you

581
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:14,310
and get in our way.

582
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:18,040
"Our"?

583
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,110
Yes.

584
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:25,920
Yes.

585
00:31:26,490 --> 00:31:27,130
"Our."

586
00:31:47,630 --> 00:31:49,560
Why are you looking at me like that?

587
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:51,200
Nothing.

588
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:53,760
I'm just not used to it.

589
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:57,440
Not used to Bai Li's soul

590
00:31:58,150 --> 00:31:59,750
being in Ning Mochen's body?

591
00:32:03,450 --> 00:32:05,230
I wasn't used to it at first.

592
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:08,510
I even wondered if I was crazy.

593
00:32:09,670 --> 00:32:11,550
It took me a long time

594
00:32:12,710 --> 00:32:14,150
to get used to this body.

595
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,600
Now that I think about it,

596
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:18,020
at that time,

597
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:20,660
I should have recognized you right away.

598
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,480
But I was too stupid.

599
00:32:24,870 --> 00:32:26,070
Sorry, Su Yu.

600
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:30,830
I used Ning Mochen’s body to work with you.

601
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:32,420
I used you

602
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:34,560
to get revenge on Ye Yunkai.

603
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:35,890
No, Bai Li.

604
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,300
I'm the one who should apologize.

605
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:42,170
I should have recognized you from the beginning.

606
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:44,690
I thought of you as Ning Mochen

607
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:46,370
and got angry at you.

608
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:49,390
That was when you were the weakest.

609
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:51,490
You must've felt helpless.

610
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:52,830
I'm sorry.

611
00:32:53,330 --> 00:32:56,190
You didn't know who I was back then.

612
00:32:57,460 --> 00:32:59,880
And that's also why

613
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:02,800
I can find out about your feelings towards me.

614
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:08,360
Thank you, Su Yu.

615
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:13,430
Now that I think about it,

616
00:33:14,210 --> 00:33:16,170
if it hadn't happened,

617
00:33:16,970 --> 00:33:19,710
I might still be the Bai Li who

618
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:22,100
hides in a lie and can't find myself.

619
00:33:22,390 --> 00:33:24,450
Thank you for helping me find myself.

620
00:33:26,830 --> 00:33:27,390
Let's go.

621
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,360
Where did you go at that time?

622
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:55,190
-Why didn’t you tell me?
-I went to find you.

623
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:57,180
If you told me, there wouldn't be so much trouble.
